snippet.title: Icarus: No Rescue
snippet.description:
ICARUS is a session-based PvE survival game for up to eight co-op players or solo. 
Explore a savage alien wilderness in the aftermath of terraforming gone wrong. 
Survive long enough to mine exotic matter, then return to orbit to craft more advanced tech. 
Meet your deadline or be left behind forever.

Watch the latest documentary, Icarus - Fatal Sky:
https://youtu.be/SIz-6-w_fxY

Buy Icarus now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149460/ICARUS/

Join our Discord:
https://discord.com/invite/surviveicarus

Follow us on Twitch:
https://www.twitch.tv/surviveicarus
